com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models

Class ListQueuesResult.Queue

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.microsoft.windowsazure.services.queue.models.ListQueuesResult.Queue
  • Enclosing class:
    ListQueuesResult

    public static class ListQueuesResult.Queue
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a queue in the storage account returned by the server. A ListQueuesResult.Queue instance contains a copy of the queue name, URI, and metadata in the storage service as of the time the queue was requested.
